; Regression test for issue #1680: Account assertions not checked for automated postings
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1680
;
; An account assertion (assert amount >= 0.00 EUR) should fire when an automated
; transaction creates postings that violate it. Currently, the assertion is silently
; ignored for automated postings, resulting in a negative balance with no error.

account Budget:Food
    assert amount >= 0.00 EUR

= /Expenses:Food/
    Budget:Food                       -1.0
    Budget:Unbudgeted                  1.0

2018-06-13 * Groceries store
    Assets:Bank:Checking               -700 EUR
    Expenses:Food                       700 EUR

test bal Budget:Food
         -700.00 EUR  Budget:Food
end test
